posts.caption: Virtual Reality Build Night
posts.description:
We are partnering with @[37681991912:274:Instructables] for our October 2014 build night. @[105269252845246:274:DODOcase] recently developed a Smartphone Virtual Reality Viewer inspired by @[308669785976849:274:Google Cardboard].

Join us this Friday at Cairo Hackerspace to explore Virtual Reality with DODOcase VR kits , bring an android or iphone .

Everyone have a chance to win a VR kit from Cairo Hackerspace , just hack ,develop software or make physical mods for the DODOcase VR kit .

Build Night Price:
Members : Free
Non-members: 20 L:E
